quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  6,42,"Daabi, Ɔno nko ara na mobesu afrε no, na sε εyε Nepε a W’ayi deε enti moresu frε no no afri mo so, na (saa berε no) mowerε befri deε mode bataa Neho no"
  6,43,Ampa sε Yε’somaa asomafoͻ kͻͻ aman-aman a wͻ’dii w’anim kan no hͻ. Na Yε’de ͻhaw ne ahokyerε too wͻn so sεdeε wͻ’bεbrε wͻn ho aseε
  6,44,"Adεn na Yε’haw no baa wͻn soͻ no w’ammerε wͻn ho aseε, na mmom wͻn akoma yεε den? Ɔbonsam maa dwuma a na wͻ’die no yεε wͻn (ani so) fε"
  6,45,"Na εberε a wͻn werε frii (afutuo) a yεde tuu wͻn no, Ye’buee (anigyedeε) biara ho pono (kwan) maa wͻn, kosii εberε a wͻn wͻ anigyeε mu wͻ deε yεde ama wͻn no mu no, Yε’sͻͻ wͻn mu mpofire mu, na hwε, wͻ’nuu wͻn ho dii awerεhoͻ"
  6,46,"Enti yεmaa amanfoͻ no a wͻ’dii bͻne no akyiri kwan yerae. Aseda wͻ Nyankopͻn, Abͻdeε nyinaa Wura no"
  6,47,"(Nkͻmhyεni), ka sε: “Modwen ho sεn? “Sε Nyankopͻn si mo aso na Ofira moani na Otua moakoma ano a, Awurade bεn na ͻwͻ Nyankopͻn akyi a anka ͻde (aso ne ani ne akoma) bεma mo?” Hwε sεdeε Yε’si kyerεkyerε nsεm no mu nanso wͻ’dane wͻn ho fri ho"
  6,48,"Ka sε “Modwene ho sεn?“ sε Nyankopͻn asotwee ba moso (anadwo) mpofire mu, anaa (awia) pefee mu a, εnyε amanfoͻ abͻneεfoͻ no na yεbεsεe wͻn?”"
  6,49,"Deε nti Yε’soma asomafoͻ no ne sε, wͻ’de (Soro Aheman no mu) anigyesεm no ho anohoba bεbͻ (amanfoͻ) na (wͻ’de Amanehunu gya no nso ho asεm) bεbͻ wͻn kͻkͻ. Enti obi a ͻbεgye adie na w’atoto ntotoeε pa no (saa Da no) ehu biara mma wͻn so, na wͻn werε nso nnho"
  6,50,"Wͻn nso a wͻ’po Yεn nsεnkyerεnee no deε, asotwee no bεka wͻn, εnam wͻn bɔne a wͻ’diiε ho nti"